(2, 'football-coaching-with-drh', 'course-listing/tennis?&cat=4', 'MKTC  courses explained', '<p>Our DRH tennis coaching courses at Milton Keynes Tennis Club run termly. The terms mirror the school terms with Spring, Summer and Autumn. Each course runs weekly with the exception of the half terms and school holidays.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe courses are split by age group and standard.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>AGES:</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Mini Tots</strong> - Ages 3/4<br />\r\n<strong>Mini Red</strong> - Ages 5-8<br />\r\n<strong>Mini Orange</strong> - Ages 8/9<br />\r\n<strong>Mini Green</strong> - Ages 10<br />\r\n<strong>Junior </strong>- Ages 11-17<br />\r\n<strong>Adults</strong> for those ages 18+.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>LEVELS:</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Club </strong>- Either new to tennis or still learning the basics. Not yet able to play matches.<br />\r\n<strong>Development </strong>- Can understand and perform all the basics in tennis and is of a level to start playing matches.<br />\r\n<strong>Team </strong>- Has experience in playing matches and also plays more than once per week. Ideally including 1to1 lessons.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '#001642', 1, 3, '2020-03-20 04:44:40', '2020-12-12 11:04:09'),
(4, 'coaching-with-drh', 'book-a-camp', 'How to make a booking', '<p>DRH Sports has teamed up with the MK City Colts FC to offer not just fantastic junior football coaching, but to provide a seamless link into teams and competition.</p>', '#001642', 1, 4, '2020-03-20 06:16:29', '2020-12-12 11:04:17'),
