(69, 'our-courses-explained', 'course-listing/tennis?&cat=7', 'LSTC  courses & timetable', '<p>Our coaching programmes mirror the school terms with Spring, Summer and Autumn term running each year. The length of the terms will differ however they will all consist of all the important elements of tennis teaching. The programmes will only run during the school term time so most coaching courses will stop during the school holidays (some adult courses may continue).&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:18px;">Here are the timetables for the Spring term 2021</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '#001642', 1, 7, '2020-11-18 11:12:38', '2020-12-12 10:10:53'),
