(8, 133, '1603283759.jpg', 'Dominic11', 'Ross-Hurst111', 'Milton Keynes Tennis Club & Letchworth Sports & Tennis Club11', '3', 'I have been a tennis coach for over 15 years and have worked with all age groups and abilities. I was previously a professional tennis player achieving a world ranking and being lucky enough to travel all over the world to compete in tournaments. \r\n\r\nI now have a passion for developing performance tennis players and helping them achieve their goals. I believe that with hard work, determination and a love for the game, anything is possible!', '2020-04-29 23:59:00', '2021-01-25 00:27:54'),
