></span></span></span></span></span></strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Useful Contacts:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>For programme&nbsp;enquiries -&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;please contact us at tenniscoaching@drhsports.co.uk / 07901903520<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>For website enquiries -&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;contact info@drhsports.co.uk<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>For urgent programme issues -&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;contact Head Coach Dominic Ross-Hurst at 07929 341226</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Player1', 99, '', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>How to book this course: </strong></span><br />\r\n- Please select the person within your account that you wish to enrol on the course.<br />\r\n- If the persons name does not appear, please check their DOB is correct for this course.<br />\r\n- Only those people listed within your account with the correct DOB will show in the drop down list.&nbsp;<br />\r\n- Only tennis club members can book this course. Please ensure that the participant is a member before attending the first session. You can register for tennis club membership <a href="https://clubspark.lta.org.uk/MiltonKeynesTennisClub/Membership/Join">HERE</a>.</p>', 133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 16, '2021-04-30', 1, '2020-12-11 08:04:45', '2020-12-17 16:45:11');
