an></strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Useful Contacts:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>For programme enquiries - </strong> please contact us at lstccoaching@drhsports.co.uk / 07901 903520<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>For website enquiries - </strong> contact info@drhsports.co.uk</span></p>', 'Player1', 76.5, '', '<p><strong>How to book this course: </strong><br />\r\n- Please select the person within your account that you wish to enrol on the course.<br />\r\n- If the persons name does not appear, please check their DOB is correct for this course.<br />\r\n- Only those people listed within your account with the correct DOB will show in the drop down list.&nbsp;</p>', 133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 29, '2021-04-30', 1, '2020-12-12 04:31:26', '2020-12-30 20:44:53'),
(97, 'lstc-adult-improvers-fri-9-30-11am', '<p style="text-align: center;">This <strong>Adult Improvers +&nbsp;</strong>coaching course is for players aged 18+&nbsp;years old who are in the intermediate stage of their tennis development.</p>', 'LSTC - Adult Improvers + - Fri 11am-12.30pm', 14, '156', 2, '168', 7, 1, 'Intermediate', '1607766372.png', '', '6 Weeks: Jan 8th, 15th, 22nd, 29th. Feb 5th, 12th', 'Letchworth Sports & Tennis Club, Muddy Lane, Letchworth, SG6 3TB', 'Friday 11am-12.30pm', '18 - 99', '8', '<p><strong>Term begins</strong>: Week commencing Jan&nbsp;4th and runs for <strong>6</strong> weeks<br />\r\n<strong>Session Dates:&nbsp;</strong>Jan 8th, 15th, 22nd, 29th. Feb 5th, 12th<br />\r\nThere will be no coaching during half term (Feb&nbsp;15th - 21st&nbsp;2021)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>This group is more advanced than&nbsp;the earlier Friday morning coaching group.</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis group is for anyone aged 18+ including those new to the game of tennis. Over the term you will be taught the basics in tennis. Grips and the Path/Angle/Speed (PAS) of the racket for all groundstroke shots and serve will be covered. Alongside this you will also be taught the basics in tactical play such as the 5 different game situations (serving, returning serve, both players at the baseline, approaching the net, passing your opponent).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo sign up for LSTC membership, please call the reception on 01462 675444</p>', '<p><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Term Dates:</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Term begins - </strong>Monday January 4th 2021<br />\r\n<strong>Half Term - </strong>Monday February 15th - Sunday February 21st 2021<br />\r\n<strong>Term Ends - </strong>Sunday March 28th 2021</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Please note: </strong>The adult coaching course that you have purchased is only for 6 wee