or: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">There is no substitute&nbsp;for regular play. The best way to improve and progress is to play more often. Those who attend multiple coaching classes and have 1to1 lessons will improve the fastest. If you&#39;re interested in attending more than one coaching class per week, starting 1to1 lessons or have any questions about your or your child&#39;s development then please speak with your group class coach.</font></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Individual lessons:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px;">Our DRH Sports tennis coaches offer 1to1 lessons for all those who want to take their development to the next level. Whilst the groups classes are essential for learning not only the basics in technique and tactics, every player is different, and therefore will have different requirements. 1to1 lessons give our team the opportunity to work more closely with players and give them bespoke advice and instruction that will enable their game to improve more quickly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe recommend that all players look at getting some 1to1 lessons at some point in their tennis journey so if this is something that interests you, please speak with your session coach or email tenniscoaching@drhsports.co.uk.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Feedback:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><font color="#000000"><font face="helvetica neue, helvetica, arial, verdana, sans-serif"><font style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initia