(946, 0, 'foot_lan_act2_description', '<p>In order to progress and suceed at anything in life, you must dedicate your time, effort and energy consistently. By doing this, no matter whether it&#39;s at tennis, another sport or at school/work, you&#39;ll improve and are more likely to suceed. Dedication is arguably the most important aspect of tennis development.&nbsp;<a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(947, 0, 'foot_lan_act3_image', '1607520297foot_lan_act3_image.png', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:54:57'),
(948, 0, 'foot_lan_act3_title', 'Fairplay', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(949, 0, 'foot_lan_act3_description', '<p>Fairplay is an absolute must within our DRH programmes. Whether it be with decision, the score or a players on and off court, pitch or playing surface, we strongly believe that all players should put fairplay at the forefront of their thoughts when playing the game.&nbsp;<a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(950, 0, 'foot_lan_act4_image', '1607520297foot_lan_act4_image.png', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:54:57'),
(951, 0, 'foot_lan_act4_title', 'Respect', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(952, 0, 'foot_lan_act4_description', '<p>Respect in sport can come in many forms. Having respect for yourself, your opponents, your teammates, your coach and others who support you is key. We always want to promote players being humble on the court so having respect for yourself and others is an important ingredient in this process.&nbsp;<a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a>1</p>', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:52:24'),
(953, 0, 'foot_lan_act5_image', '1607520297foot_lan_act5_image.png', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:54:57'),
(954, 0, 'foot_lan_act5_title', 'Leadership', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(955, 0, 'foot_lan_act5_description', '<p>Leadership is an important attribute for us at DRH Sports. Although not necessarily a quality you would normally associate to tennis, becoming a capable leader allows a player&rsquo;s confidence to grow alongside their ability to manage responsibilities.&nbsp;<a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
