(1062, 0, 'coach_listing_desc', '<p style="text-align: center;">Welcome to the DRH Sports Coach Connect page. On this page you&#39;ll find all the tennis coaches that have not only registered with us at DRH Sports but are also able to be linked to.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll you have to do is to locate your coach, view their profile and send them a link request. Want to know how to interact with your coach? Visit our <a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/tennis-pro">DRH Tennis Pro</a> page for more information.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><strong>Please Note:</strong></span> Our Coach Connect feature is meant for players to link with their existing tennis coach, not to find a new tennis coach. The feature is designed to enhance an already existing coach / player relationship. We advise that you contact the tennis coach before sending them a link request - Thank you</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="gtx-trans" style="position: absolute; left: 339px; top: -5.33333px;">\r\n<div class="gtx-trans-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', 'coach-listing', NULL, '2020-05-27 00:10:07', '2020-12-27 23:46:00'),
