(1095, 0, 'goals_desc', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Welcome to the DRH Tennis Pro - Goals</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is where a player can enter their first set of goals. There are 4 sections, MY BIG DREAMS, then <strong>SHORT, MEDIUM AND LONG TERM</strong> goals sections. Each section represents a something you want to achieve, but in a different timeframe. These goals do not have to be tennis related but are meant to act as a way to trying to start your goal setting journey. Once you have uploaded your goals, your coach (if you are linked to them) will be able to see your goals and can give comments on them. You can then work with your coach to create the correct goals before you finalise them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once your goals are finalised, they cannot be changed. However you can always create a new set of goals once you have finalised the previous set. If you want to find out more about how our Tennis Pro feature works, please <a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/tennis-pro"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>click here</strong></span></a>. If you have any questions about how the DRH Tennis Pro feautre works, email us at tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'badges', NULL, '2020-06-09 00:37:28', '2020-11-21 07:40:23'),
