(1128, 0, 'childcare_content', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">To find the reference number for your specific childcare voucher provider please go to our&nbsp;<a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/faqs.html" target="_blank">FAQS</a>&nbsp;page</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">After confirming your booking you will need to follow through with the payment within 48 hours otherwise the booking will be invalid. You will need to log into your childcare voucher portal to complete the payment. Payments using Tax Free Childcare must be made 10 days prior to your child attending the camp.</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Your child will only be added to the registers once payment of the correct amount has been received and confirmed.</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">If your childcare voucher provider is not listed below or if you have any question, please email info@drhsports.co.uk</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'child-care-popup', NULL, '2020-07-09 02:48:34', '2020-07-27 06:02:12'),
