(1133, 0, 'report1_content', '<p><span style="font-size:22px;"><b>Welcome Coach!</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This section is where you can upload your end of term reports for the players that are within your group classes. You will only be able to see and send reports to players that are enrolled in a group class that you are linked with (DRH Sports will have linked you with the group class if it&#39;s one that you teach).&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here&#39;s what you need to do....</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1) </strong>Select the term and the course (if the course is not linked with that particular term, then it will not show).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2) </strong>Select the name of the player you wish to send the report to (Only players enrolled on the course via the DRH system will show in the list) and click the SUBMIT button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3)</strong> If the player has already had a report written for them in this group and term, then you will see the historical data previously added.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4) </strong>Tick the boxes that apply to the player. If a section does not apply to the player, then leave it blank - it will show with a red cross next to it when the player see&#39;s the report.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5)</strong> Add your comments at the bottom of the report.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Please Note:</strong> If the player has taken part in any mid term skills tests, then their test scores will be shown at the bottom of the page. You may want to refer to these scores within your report. Please ensure that what you write reflects the positive elements of the players game and helps to motivate them to keep working hard to achieve their goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions about questions about this feature, please email DRH Sports at tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>', 'report', NULL, '2020-07-10 05:28:54', '2020-11-22 17:15:37'),
(1134, 0, 'report2_content', '<p><span style="font-size:22px;"><b>Welcome Coach!</b></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This page allows you to create a report for any player who is directly linked to you via our system This&nbsp;<strong>Player Report</strong>&nbsp;gives you an open section to wirte as much or as little as you like about your player. We recommend that you&nbsp; include feedback about all the elements in your player&#39;s game including mental / physical / tactical / technical within this report. You can send a player report to linked players as many times as you wish.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>1) </strong>Select the player you wish to send the report to - Only players directly linked to you will show in the list.<br />\r\n<strong>2)</strong> Click submit - if you have sent&nbsp;<strong>Player Reports</strong>&nbsp;for this player previously, they will be shown underneath.<br />\r\n<strong>3)</strong> Add in your report and click submit - You&#39;ll have to confirm the report before it is sent.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have any questions about questions about this feature, please email DRH Sports at tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>', 'report', NULL, '2020-07-10 05:28:55', '2020-11-22 17:16:23'),
(1135, 0, 'report_detail', '<p>Dear player,&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease see your&nbsp;<strong>End of Term&nbsp;</strong>report below. This has been sent to you from your group tennis coach and outlines how you&#39;ve done over the last few months.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have&nbsp;taken part in any of our mid-term skills tests, then your results will be listed at the bottom of the page along with any additional comments from your coach.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWell done for all your efforts over the term. Keep working hard to achieve you your tennis goals.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDRH Sports<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'report', NULL, '2020-07-10 05:28:55', '2020-11-23 05:25:55'),
