(1152, 0, 'report3_content', '<p style="margin-bottom:12.0pt"><b><span style="font-size:16.5pt">Welcome!</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our match report system brings a unique way to give feedback to tennis players. Not only can you create a competition, but you can create multiple match reports, add match details, scores and feedback. You can also add in any match charting and match stat data. Our system will then be able to show you the match stats for your player. Here&#39;s what you need to do:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>1) </strong>Select the player from the list and create the competition (if you are a parent or player, only people listed in your account will show. If you are a coach then only players linked to you will show). Then click SUBMIT.<br />\r\n<strong>2)</strong> Create the first match, include the details along with your feedback about what went well, what could be improved and any further feedback.<br />\r\n<strong>3) </strong>Upload match charting images if you wish. You don&#39;t have to do this, but it can be good to show a player if you have them.<br />\r\n<strong>4) </strong>Click SUBMIT - You&#39;ll then see the match linked to the competition and can add another match if you wish. You can also then go the match you have just entered and add in the match stats.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe hope you enjoy this and all the other DRH Tennis Pro features. If you have any questions or feedback for us, just let us know at tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>', 'report', NULL, '2020-08-05 01:01:38', '2020-11-24 10:19:28'),
