(1166, 0, 'match_stats_text', 'Please enter the stats for the match you have charted below. After entering the requested data, our system will calculate the percentage and average calculations. \r\n\r\nPlease Note - \r\n\r\n1) If you do not know or do not have the data for any of the sections then it is better that you enter a number you think is close to the accurate value. Entering a zero value will have negative consequences to the final statistics. We recommend that unless you are confident that you know all the initial data, it might be best not to upload the stats. \r\n\r\n2) If you enter any of the values incorrectly, you will be able to come back and update the values.\r\n\r\n3) If you have charted the player using pen and paper, there is the option of uploading the image so that the linked coach or player can view.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions regarding this feature, please email us at tennispro@drhsports.co.uk', 'general-setting', NULL, '2020-08-13 06:30:55', '2020-11-19 11:21:17'),
