(1325, 0, '', 'There are 4 sections, MY BIG DREAMS, then SHORT, MEDIUM AND LONG TERM goals sections. Each section represents a something you want to achieve, but in a different timeframe. These goals do not have to be tennis related but are meant to act as a way to trying to start your goal setting journey.', 'badges', NULL, '2020-11-19 08:50:51', '2020-11-19 08:50:51'),
(1326, 0, 'report_desc', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Welcome to DRH Tennis Pro - Reports</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this section you can view the reports that have been sent to your players by their group or linked coach. If a player is currently enrolled on a coaching course with DRH Sports, then the coach linked to the class will send the players end of term reports here. You will see the report appear in this section and you will also get a notification via email.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If a player in your account is linked directly to a coach in our system, then that coach can also send the player a Player Report. This is an open report that gives the coach more freedom to write more in-depth reports about the players game, their progress and what they need to do to continue their improvement. Like the End of Term report, you will receive an email notifying you of any new reports.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to find out more about how our Tennis Pro feature works, please <a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/tennis-pro"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>click here</strong></span></a>. If you have any questions about this section, please email tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>', 'badges', NULL, '2020-11-19 08:53:46', '2020-11-21 07:40:23'),
(1327, 0, 'matches_desc', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Welcome to DRH Tennis Pro - Matches</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our unique matches section allows players registered with DRH Sports to upload information about their recent tennis competitions and matches, create reports, add match feedback, upload match charting and view stats about each match.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the player uploads a match report and is linked to a coach via our system, then that coach can see that report along with any additional information that has been uploaded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Did you know that your linked coach can also upload matches for their linked players and can include feedback, match charting and match stats. If you want to find out more about how our Tennis Pro feature works, please <a href="http://49.249.236.30:8654/dominic-new/tennis-pro"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>click here</strong></span></a>. if you have any questions, please email tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'badges', NULL, '2020-11-19 08:53:46', '2020-11-21 07:40:23'),
