(17, 'home-page', 'ada-ngai', 'My five year old boy enjoyed going to the Multisport camp very much ! The coaches are all very friendly and made him feel welcome.', 'Ada Ngai', '', 1, '2020-12-05 12:50:19', '2020-12-05 12:50:19'),
